        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="subsq original-text" data-text-version="original" id="orig-paragraph-0031">In all,</p>
      <p class="subsq transformed-text hidden" data-text-version="transformed" id="trans-paragraph-0031">In total,</p>
      <p class="receipt-item original-text" data-text-version="original" id="orig-paragraph-0032">$14.72½</p>
      <p class="receipt-item transformed-text" data-text-version="transformed" id="trans-paragraph-0032">$14.73</p>
      <p class="subsq original-text" data-text-version="original" id="orig-paragraph-0033">My income was (patrem familias vendacem, non emacem esse oportet), from</p>
      <p class="subsq transformed-text hidden" data-text-version="transformed" id="trans-paragraph-0033">My income came from (a father should be good at selling, not buying),</p>
      <div class="alignment-block alignment-block-align-left inset-block">
        <div class="receipt-row">
          <p class="receipt-item original-text" data-text-version="original" id="orig-paragraph-0034">Nine bushels and twelve quarts of beans sold,</p>
          <p class="receipt-item transformed-text" data-text-version="transformed" id="trans-paragraph-0034">Nine bushels and twelve quarts of beans were sold.</p>
          <p class="receipt-item original-text" data-text-version="original" id="orig-paragraph-0035">$16.94</p>
          <p class="receipt-item transformed-text" data-text-version="transformed" id="trans-paragraph-0035">$16.94</p>
        </div>
        <div class="receipt-row">
          <p class="receipt-item original-text" data-text-version="original" id="orig-paragraph-0036">Five large potatoes,</p>
          <p class="receipt-item transformed-text" data-text-version="transformed" id="trans-paragraph-0036">Five big potatoes,</p>
